The #4 round is that the ideal “go to brush” for face/body artists of all ability levels for everything from fine to thick lines, just by variable your pressure. excellent teardrops, swirls and lines 1st time, every time.
 Designed by a victory body artist to exactly meet the unique desires of the face and body painters, these superior Golden Taklon brushes have that all-important firm spring-back and shorter bristle length, supplying you with most management over your linework. These long-lasting brushes have black acrylic handles (no flaking like wood handles!), a tapered handle for sectioning paints and densely packed nickel plated ferrules that leaves no area for water and paint to get cornered – creating them simply to wash, and fast and hygienical to dry.
